videos.description: West Virginia's Emmitt Matthews Jr. catches the bad pass from Matt Mooney and goes on a one-man fast break for the dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Errant pass leads to monster and-1 dunk) 2019/03/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Errant pass leads to monster and-1 dunk

videos.description: Texas Tech's Matt Mooney throws up the alley-oop pass to a cutting Tariq Owens for the jam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Owens slams home the lob from Mooney) 2019/03/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Owens slams home the lob from Mooney

videos.description: Jarrett Culver blocks the shot, corrals the rebound, an takes it all the way for the and-1 layup, as Texas Tech goes on a 22-5 run to take the lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Culver blocks the shot then hits the layup for the lead) 2019/03/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Culver blocks the shot then hits the layup for the lead

videos.description: Jermaine Haley makes the and-1 layup off the dish from Lamont West to cement a West Virginia lead they never lost, beating Texas Tech 79-74

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Haley powers through defender for go-ahead bucket) 2019/03/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Haley powers through defender for go-ahead bucket

videos.description: West Virginia fights off a late 22-5 point run by Texas Tech to win 79-74, becoming the first 10 seed to reach the Big 12 semifinals.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (West Virginia finishes historic upset vs. Texas Tech) 2019/3/14 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: West Virginia finishes historic upset vs. Texas Tech
